{"word":"ἀναφύρω","slug":"ἀναφύρω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναφύρω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to mix up, confound:—</i> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ἦν πάντα ἀναπεφυρμένα</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to defile</i>, <el>αἵματι ἀναπεφυρμένος</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}